    G2[Doc Hygiene]
    G3[Backlog Hygiene]
  end

  subgraph Tests
    X1[RatchetTest.cs]
    X2[ArchitectureRules.cs]
    X3[LoadTest.cs]
    X4[SnapshotTest.cs]
    X5[PiiGuardTest.cs]
    X6[VersionAuditTest.cs]
  end

  %% === CONTEXT ROT (obstacle) — compensated by stateless guardrails ===
  O1 -->|causes| T1
  O1 -->|causes| T3
  O1 -->|causes| T8
  X1 -->|compensates| O1
  X2 -->|compensates| O1
  X5 -->|compensates| O1
  X6 -->|compensates| O1
